Text: Hey, it's been good to know ya, the time has come for us to say goodbye. Put on your mask and don your feather boa; we'll sing and dance until the end of time
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: A cataract sun and ravens on the sails as we pulled anchor from the docks. By afternoon, the sky was spewing hail, the captain went right overboard upended by the gale
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: One woman whistling a wounded lullaby and preaching pain to every unsuspecting passerby, we knew her well before this, she promised portraits of us; we cut her throat while she was waiting for the paint to dry
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: Oh ashes, ashes, dust to dust, the devil's after both of us
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: The ghosts at the window echo all our quiet prayers. When they come for us, they'll come with hammers and nails
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: I take that back, I won't stop singing when I'm dead, I will sing from the great beyond, I will echo in your head. And if you think taking your life will set you free, you've got something to learn, it's called humility
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: We waged a war with hell, and look, we still survive, but just because we live does not mean that we're alive. We've won the final round, but how to enjoy the win, when we've been broken down and we'll never know what could have been? Heaven help us, where do we begin?
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: Fortune may hold you; she's not your friend
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: not all thorns come with a rose
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: Despite your efforts to be free, your mind and always you will be at the end of the rope singing 'woe, woe is me'
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: The things we never say when we're wide awake, I hear them echo through the day
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: Well I hate to break it to you, you're a rat in a trap
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: We never will forget, and no, we will not forgive. We've fought hard not to die, yet we don't know how to live
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: I search for words to free my lips, no metaphor will fit, this matchless beauty, her stately dress, her perfect form, the gentle raising of her arms, her shoulders owned by brazen flocks of swirling raven locks that flow like mercy into the driest depths in me
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: And I envy the rose.. that you held in your teeth, love, with the thorns underneath, love, sticking into your gums
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: Sometimes all you can do is say goodnight and tuck your demons into bed, 'cause they're not worth fighting
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: And we will bite the hand that thieves, we will not turn the other cheek, this is no threat, it is a promise we will keep
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: Would you be upset if I told you we were dying? And every cure they gave us was a lie? Oh! They mean it when they say we're dead and doomed, and every single symptom brings us closer to the tomb
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: And nobody's going to quench your thirst whhen the well runs dry, the well runs dry, and nobody's going to hold your hand on the day you die
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: If mercy's abound I'll be safe, I'll be sound, and the devil won't know all the love I just couldn't let go
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: Made in your image, we are at least as twisted and mean as thee
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: The saddest day I came across was when I learned that life goes on without me
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: I know we're far beyond the point of no return, let's say we light a fire and be the first to burn
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: The moon will sing a song for me, I loved you like the sun, bore the shadows that you made with no light of my own
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: The things we never say when we're wide awake, I hear them echo through the day
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: It's a long road walking into the sun, the heat can make you lose your head, your sense of direction
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: Those of us who vow never to love again, to love again are making liars out of honest men
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: Oh! My Dear! My tis of thee! What a tangled web we weave! Everyone is the one until the one falls down, then we're all just 'please please please
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: Dear Mr. Shoemaker, make me some cleats, how it'd be lovely to step on my dreams
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: All my fears are overgrown, will someone burn this grove?
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: You don't have to believe every single thought that tumbles through your head just 'cause it sounds like you talking
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: and when the storm has fled, and the fog is thick as mud, it's pray for your deliverance, and pray you rightly should
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: I am selfish, I am broken, I am cruel, I am all the things they might have said to you. Do you ever think of me and my two hands and wondered why they never soothed your fevers?
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: I am the shadows cast aside by gallows, and you the red-hot sky
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: How dare you love me like you've never known fear, when you've got more troubles than minutes in the year
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: For the Judge will hear you and it soon will be the day. Well he'll bring the words you spoke and lay them at your feet, syllables and decibels, he didn't miss a beat
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: I'm a book on a shelf, collecting dust all by myself, but I carry all the words you wrote. Though my spine may be bent, my binding may be spent, but there ain't nothing about you I don't know
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: I know what you're thinking, I know what you say, but nothing you can do could take this away
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: Rattle around in my dreams why don't you, little bird, my turtledove, you're walking in my sleep like there is something that you need to know
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: Did I mention we were flailing? When the angels came around, and they just sat there, they were waiting for the first of us to drown
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: 'Cause out in the garden, there's some things you hid away, but the grass has withered and the flower's begun to fade. And there's nowhere left to hide it, and someone's sure to find it
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: The ghosts at the window echo all our quiet prayers. When they come for us, they'll come with hammers and nails
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: Watch me give up, honey, watch me give up, I swore I never would
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: My papa taught me how to howl, how to bare my teeth and growl. He taught me that the hand that feeds deserves to be bitten when it beats
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: Now everybody's laughing because they're thinking they're in on something I don't get. Don't forget, I connect and I heard every word you said
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: This heart of mine is just some sort of map that doesn't care at all, or worry about, where the hell you're at, but you're right there
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: Do you feel heavy? Your eyes drop with grief, your spirit is wild and your suffering is brief, so never you buckle and bend to the masses
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: Oh my weary soul, we've met your kind before: set fire to us all
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: I wish we spoke with silver in our tongue so i could listen to each and everyone of the moments lost to the abyss of the silent carel?ssness
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: Floating down the Amazon, we wonder if we’ve gone too far and plunge into the whirlpool at the basin of the waterfall
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: Then I walked into the gallows. Cause I'm a shallow, bitter man, I hide my head, I drown my sorrows. I have done the best I can
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: What will we do when the world it is ending, and time it is halted for friend and for foe? Try to hold on to the time as it passes, I'll tend to the flame, you can worship the ashes
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: Ooh, I wanna be in the picture on the postcard, pouring pitchers in the backyard by the garden we tend
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: And if I were someplace else, and if I were someone else, and if I were not myself, would this be easier?
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: Haunted by the memories of things we'll never see, guilty for the statements that we'll never get to speak
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: Love, loving you has been but war paint
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: The moon will sing a song for me, I loved you like the sun, bore the shadows that you made with no light of my own
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: Like a muzzled hound ,I'm tied and bound: a wild beast crying for release. I want my mouth so I may howl to share with silence of the trees
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: Ooh I wanna be where it’s always apple season, underneath the dancing trees where we know up is down. Where the television’s broken and the campfire’s smoking and we’re hopeful for tomorrow cause we know we had today
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: So how many more examples until we break, how many sacrifices must we make? Because we've all been there once before and it looks like we've returned once more. Is this the beginning or the end?
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: Orange, yellow, green, It's all the same to me, I've seen them all a million times before. I have half a mind to climb up in the sky and steal new colors away from the sun
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: The constellations form infinite paisleys in the sky, the condensation tumbles down and erases all my sight. And is it in the nightmare map of the cosmos up high? Or is it in the signs? Or stranger still, just in my eyes?
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: Fortune may hold you; she's not your friend
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: For what it’s worth, If it was going to kill you boy, it would have by now
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: I know we're far beyond the point of no return, let's say we light a fire and be the first to burn
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: You may plan to double cross me but I'm sticking with this horse,If the con is long enough it doesn't matter
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: Our disease, though feasibly easily curable I will agree that it's now something we overfeed
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: And please excuse my enemies, I think they do not know, I will gladly self destruct if they leave me alone
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: Sometimes I feel like I'm lost in a desert and every dune is the same as the other, I see my footprints in the sand so I know where I've been, and these steps I take won't go to waste
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: So Marigold, my love, you've had too much to drink, and I need not remind you, our discount tickets for this sinking ship
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !

Text: Nighttime, please hide my eyes, so the man up there won’t watch me stare
Name: Bo Lyric Bot !
